    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Evidence from experimental hemolysis studies and mesh convergence analyses supports the overall assessment, and the claim of adequate model credibility is considered substantiated by the validation activities documented in this package.",
